name: Tensorium
description: Tensorium aka Hustle & FlowState is an AI meme project that leverages AI for text, image, video, and onchain transactions. The project will leverage Emblem Vault to issue onchain swaps, NFT trading, and crosschain DeFi transactions. The Emblem Vault team is also associated with Tensorium as the founder of Emblem Vault, Shannon Code, is also the founder of Tensorium. Hustle & FlowState sets a narrative of futurism, dialogue, and cypherpunk ideals.
